To run all tests: ./manage.py test similarity/tests/
Searches for all files in the directory similarity/tests/ that matches the pattern test*.py

To run one test file: ./manage.py test similarity.tests.modulename
e.g. ./manage.py test similarity.tests.test_fingerprint

To run one unit test: ./manage.py test similarity.tests.modulename.classname.testname
e.g. ./manage.py test similarity.tests.test_fingerprint.FingerprintTest.test_fingerprint_text
